<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.8.2">
<l>munnīrai muṉṉāḷ kaṭaintāṉai mūḻttanāḷ</l>
<l>annīrai mīṉā yamaitta perumāṉai</l>
<l>teṉṉāli mēya tirumālai yemmāṉai</l>
<l>naṉṉīr vayalcūḻ naṟaiyūril kaṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I saw in Naṟaiyūr, encircled by well-watered fields,</l>
<l>The one who, in days past, churned the three-watered [sea],</l>
<l>The great lord who entered that water as a fish</l>
<l rend="indent">in the days [the earth] was sunken,</l>
<l>Our lord, Tirumāl who dwells in Teṉṉāli.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
